Netizen contribution
On July 7, it was reported online that a woman in Shanghai made insulting remarks about China in a subway car and was filmed by a 19-year-old food delivery man in the same car.
Later, when the woman tried to stop filming, the two had a conflict and the food delivery man choked the woman.
Afterwards, the official report stated that the food delivery man said that he edited the video and posted it online for the purpose of attracting fans, hoping to attract attention.
Currently, the woman has been sent to a mental health center for treatment, and the food delivery man has been administratively punished according to law.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Supplement: According to the official report, the woman was a 29-year-old mentally disabled person who came to Shanghai for medical treatment.
